Welcome To Taskserver
---------------------

This is an Inthe.AM-specific fork of the TaskServer;
see the upstream repository at [GothenburgBitFactory/taskserver.git](https://github.com/GothenburgBitFactory/taskserver).

Special Behaviors
-----------------

- Uses an external sqlite3 certificate registry for mapping user accounts to
  specific certificates.
- Emits events on a Redis pubsub queue for communicating with other services
  including:
  - `sync.<username>`: Emitted when a user synchronizes.  Includes a payload
    including performance and troubleshooting information.
  - `taskd.certificate.<username>`: Emitted when verifying a user's presented
    certifiate.  Includes information about whether that certificate was
    recognized and accepted.
